    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and it is honestly in incredible shape. It looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one\u2014it\u2019s always been garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and there isn't a single scratch or scuff to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and runs like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E92 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving S65 V8 with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precision 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution and mechanical grip. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable compression and rebound settings. Finished in pristine Alpine White over extended Novillo leather, the exterior boasts original paint depth with zero imperfections, while the undercarriage remains free of oxidation. This is a turn-key example for the discerning enthusiast seeking an uncompromising, high-RPM driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Full service history. Clean title. No accidents.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true 'time capsule' specimen, preserved in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standard. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like factory finish entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and it retains that distinct new-car aroma. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the heated seating, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a comprehensive service history where every maintenance milestone was met with precision. The undercarriage is equally clean, showing no signs of weather exposure. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle that drives with the tightness and responsiveness of a brand-new car. For the buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
